Sun, 18 Dec 2005 19:00:03 -0800  kauf:

	Changed paths:
	   M /branches/S2_0/server/civserver.c
	   M /branches/S2_0/server/score.c
	   M /branches/S2_0/server/score.h
	   M /branches/S2_0/server/srv_main.c
	   M /branches/S2_0/server/srv_main.h

	to make animated gifs for reviewing pubserver games, we currently make ppms
	of the maps from savegames, then after some manipulation, do ppm2gif to
	make the gif.

	This patch moves the ppm-making into the server. To turn it on, pass -Ppm
	to the server on the command line. The ppms are put wherever the savegames are.

	Patch by me. See PR#14827


Fri, 16 Dec 2005 19:38:17 -0800  kauf:

	Changed paths:
	   M /branches/S2_0/common/connection.h
	   M /branches/S2_0/configure.ac
