	the options_settable packet.

	Patch by me in PR#13631.

Thu Aug 11 01:30:10 2005  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* doc/BUGS:

	Known bug:

	- Using the CMA in games with a timeout will cause the client to
	track the time remaining incorrectly. The result is the turn will
	end while the client claims there is still time remaining.

	See PR#13645.

