	cause bugs when cities were transferred twice since the second
	update might not be sent.

	Reported by Benoit Hudson in PR#13437. Patch by me.

Thu Jul 21 19:32:05 2005  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* client/gui-gtk-2.0/helpdlg.c, client/gui-win32/helpdlg.c,
