	common/terrain.h, server/generator/mapgen.c, server/ruleset.c,
	server/savegame.c:

	Fix bugs with dereferencing of T_UNKNOWN, by changing such
	dereferences to be harmless: - The tile_types[] array is hidden.
	All users are changed to use get_tile_type(). - get_tile_type
	returns a dummy tile_type for T_UNKNOWN references.

	Patch by me in PR#13488.

