Sat Jan 01 22:12:45 2005  Per I. Mathisen <per@leftist.net>:

	* common/player.h, server/plrhand.c, server/stdinhand.c:

	Makes novice and /away AI go through revolution just like normal
	players. This closes a cheating loophole that players can use,
	settings themselves to /away once they get Republic, to avoid a
	period of anarchy. See PR#11667.

