Thu Dec 09 16:28:11 2004  Mike Kaufman <kaufman@orion.physics.wisc.edu>:

	* server/barbarian.c, server/citytools.c, server/cityturn.c,
	server/connecthand.c, server/diplhand.c, server/diplomats.c,
	server/gamelog.c, server/gamelog.h, server/maphand.c,
