	server/stdinhand.c, server/stdinhand.h, server/unittools.c:

	Make the gamelog XML. The intent here is to modify the gamelog so
	that usernames are associated with players and that the gamelog
	is easier to parse. Also different win scenarios (allied win,
	team win) are handled properly.

	See PR#9321. Patch by me.

