Thu Nov 25 23:27:23 2004  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* client/gui-gtk-2.0/cma_fe.c, client/gui-mui/citydlg.c,
	client/gui-sdl/cma_fe.c, client/gui-win32/cma_fe.c,
