Fri Nov 19 02:29:35 2004  Gregory Berkolaiko <Gregory.Berkolaiko@math.tamu.edu>:

	* server/diplomats.c:

	Prevent a crash caused by using a possibly invalid "improvement"
	variable in place of the valid "target" variable in
	diplomat_sabotage. Also fix the logic: the comment says that the
	targeted sabotage is twice as hard (the probability is divided by
	2). In fact the probability (which is less than one by
	definition) was squared instead.

	Issued as 11058.

