Thu Nov 18 04:17:41 2004  Gregory Berkolaiko <Gregory.Berkolaiko@math.tamu.edu>:

	* server/unithand.c:

	When an AI unit is given orders (by a human, presumably), clear
	the AI role because: * the goto dest has probably changed and a
	role assumes a goto dest with certain properties * the AI unit
	needs to notify it's partners (bodyguards, ferries) about the
	change in plans

	Reported, researched and fixed by Jason, PR#10567.

