Wed Sep 29 02:24:24 2004  Mike Kaufman <kaufman@orion.physics.wisc.edu>:

	* server/generator/utilities.h, server/sanitycheck.c,
	server/settlers.c:

	Code outside of the map tracks tiles instead of coordinates. Thus
	whole_map_iterate, map_get_terrain, etc. operate on tiles. Unit
	and city structures hold tile values rather than (x,y) pairs.

	See PR#10047. Patch by Jason Short

