Thu Sep 23 06:36:09 2004  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* server/maphand.c:

	Remove player-tile updates from send_tile_info_always(). Instead
	the caller must call update_player_tile_knowledge() separately if
	the info needs to be updated. This helps fix a bug where the
	playermap would not be correctly updated for AI players.

	Patch by Marko Lindqvist <marko.lindqvist@pp5.inet.fi> in
	PR#10190, with comment changes by me.

Thu Sep 23 00:37:27 2004  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* client/citydlg_common.c, client/citydlg_common.h,
	client/gui-gtk-2.0/cityrep.c:

	Add a new function city_queue_insert() to insert a production
	item into a city's production queue. Use this function in the
	gtk2 city report to fix problems when an unbuildable item was
	added into the queue.

	Patch by me in PR#10026.

