Fri Sep 17 09:33:52 2004  Mateusz Stefek <mstefek@poczta.fm>:

	* data/flags/Makefile.am:

	Install hobbits flag

Fri Sep 17 09:17:08 2004  Mateusz Stefek <mstefek@poczta.fm>:

	* client/connectdlg_common.c:

	After forking, we try to connect to the server for 50sec. After
	that time we assume that the server is dead or hangs. But we can
	easily check if the child exited or returned from the last
	execv(). This patch implements it. See PR#10150

Fri Sep 17 09:14:01 2004  Mateusz Stefek <mstefek@poczta.fm>:

