Fri Sep 10 21:20:53 2004  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* server/citytools.h, server/stdinhand.c:

	- Rename is_sane_name as is_ascii_name. - Move the is_ascii_name
	check into is_allowed_player_name and is_allowed_city_name. This
	means that the server will not suggest a name that cannot be
	used. - Allow a name taken from the ruleset to be used, even if
	is_ascii_name won't pass it.

	See PR#9995.

Fri Sep 10 21:20:53 2004  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

