Thu Sep 09 21:32:20 2004  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* common/terrain.c, common/terrain.h:

	Extend the count_xxx_near_tile functions to optionally return a
	percentage value rather than the number of tiles. In most cases
	the percentage is more useful because the number of tiles may
	vary between rectangular and hexagonal topologies.

	Patch by me in PR#9921.

