Tue Sep 07 23:37:41 2004  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* m4/auth.m4:

	Don't use AC_HELP_STRING since it's not supported in autoconf
	2.13.

	Patch by James Canete in PR#9943.

Tue Sep 07 23:28:47 2004  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* common/fc_types.h, common/terrain.h:

	Move the terrain enumeration values out of headers and into
	mapgen.c. These values are deprecated and no new code should use
	them.

	Patch by me in PR#9962.

