	someone else that could defend a city so that we could leave.

Sat Sep 04 16:53:39 2004  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* common/terrain.h, data/civ1/terrain.ruleset,
	data/civ2/terrain.ruleset, data/default/terrain.ruleset,
	data/history/terrain.ruleset:

