Thu Aug 26 07:59:01 2004  Mateusz Stefek <mstefek@poczta.fm>:

	* client/agents/cma_fec.h:

	We need some default cma presets available in the client. They
	will help new users understand CMA.

	With this patch "Max Food", "Max Gold", "Max Prod", "Max Science"
	and "Very happy" presets are created if there's no configuration
	file (or when it is too old)

	You have to remove "[cma]" section from your ~/.civclientrc to
	test it. Patch by me in PR#9718

