Tue Aug 24 06:51:43 2004  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* utility/ftwl/Makefile.am:

	If ftwl isn't being compiled, don't build libftwl.a. This avoids
	a problem on some compilers where it's not possible to build an
	empty library.

	Reported by Benoit Hudson <bh@techhouse.brown.edu> in PR#9494.
	Patch by Marko Lindqvist <marko.lindqvist@pp5.inet.fi>.

