Sat Aug 21 18:32:37 2004  Mike Kaufman <kaufman@orion.physics.wisc.edu>:

	* server/civserver.c, server/connecthand.c, server/srv_main.c,
	server/srv_main.h:

	Remove the capability requirement for authentication. Add three
	commandline options for the server: -a --auth Enable server
	authentication. -G --Guests Allow guests to login if auth is
	enabled. -N --Newusers Allow new users to login if auth is
	enabled.

	This allows single player mode to work correctly when
	authentication is enabled. See PR#8570.

