Wed Jul 28 16:45:03 2004  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* client/tilespec.c, client/tilespec.h:

	Use an iteration over tileset directions to load and draw corner
	sprites, rather than hard-coding each direction. This works
	better for hex tilesets and has less duplicated logic.

	Patch by me in PR#9504.

