Mon Jul 19 17:13:38 2004  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* common/map.h:

	Add a new map iterator iterate_outward_dxy. It is used by
	iterate_outward and square_dxy_iterate. This makes
	square_dxy_iterate respect "break" and allows it to work for hex
	maps.

	Patch by me in PR#9414.

