	PR#9247.

Sun Jul 18 00:43:56 2004  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* common/aicore/cm.c:

	Ignore the factor_target when calculating the fitness of a result
	in the CM. FT_EXTRA is buggy and unnecessary, so we just ignore
	it (but it is left in the API, for now).

	Patch by Benoit Hudson <bh@techhouse.brown.edu> as part of
	PR#9247.

