Fri Jul 09 17:58:51 2004  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* client/gui-xaw/citydlg.c:

	Remove the callbacks for clicking on an elvis/scientist/taxman in
	the city dialog. Instead there is just one callback that rotates
	the specialist, like is done in other clients. This removes a
	limit on the number of specialists and fixes a bug where the
	hard-coded specialist rotation wouldn't work if the ruleset was
	changed.

	Patch by me in PR#9319.

