Tue Jul 06 21:48:48 2004  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* common/unittype.c, common/unittype.h, server/savegame.c:

	Save units' types by name rather than by ID. This avoids creating
	savegame incompatability when the order of units is changed in
	the ruleset. Backwards-compatability is handled by a fixed array
	of the ordering of the old unit names in the various rulesets.

	Patch by Mateusz Stefek <mstefek@poczta.fm> in PR#9123 with
	changes by me.

