Thu Jul 01 18:15:52 2004  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* common/map.c, common/map.h:

	Change adjc_dir_iterate and cartesian_adjacent_iterate to work
	properly with topologies that have different valid and cardinal
	directions. - Both are wrappers for adjc_dirlist_iterate. - The
	lists of valid and cardinal directions is built in init_topology.

	Patch by Greg, Ross, and myself in PR#8959, with style, comment,
	and variable names changes by me.

