Mon May 24 21:42:16 2004  Per I. Mathisen <per@leftist.net>:

	* common/aicore/Makefile.am, common/aicore/citymap.c,
	common/aicore/citymap.h:

	Add citymap code to common AI code repository (common/aicore/).
	This is a large int double array that corresponds to the freeciv
	main map. It keeps track of the occupancy and crowdedness of
	tiles for settlers and cities.

