Sun May 23 02:05:37 2004  Gregory Berkolaiko <Gregory.Berkolaiko@math.tamu.edu>:

	* ai/aidata.c, ai/aidata.h, ai/aitools.c, ai/aitools.h,
	ai/aiunit.c, server/settlers.c:

	Introduce find_ferry function. It can find the nearest ferry for
	a unit which is positioned inland, the ferry can be in any sea
	adjacent to the unit's continent. It uses some powerful PF magic
	to do so.

	Issued as (PR#8777).

