	client/gui-win32/mapview.c, client/gui-xaw/mapview.c,
	client/include/mapview_g.h, client/mapview_common.c:

	Change the show_city_desc function: - It is told which canvas to
	draw to. - It tells the caller the dimensions of the city text
	that was drawn. The show_city_descriptions function is changed to
	take advantage of this. This should prevent city descriptions
	from ever being overdrawn during an update_map_canvas call.

	Patch by me in PR#8746 with added comments.

