Fri May 14 11:04:22 2004  Sebastian Bauer <mail@sebastianbauer.info>:

	* server/gamehand.c, utility/shared.c:

	Introduced a new CHALLENGE_PATH define. If set, it defines the
	path for the challenge file which needed if a client want to
	control the server.

	As AmigaOS does't know about Home directories, modified
	user_home_dir() to return a appropriate directory.

	Closes my patch #8721.

