	* client/mapview_common.c, client/mapview_common.h:

	Improve the speed of mapview scrolling. If the mapview is
	recentered any overlapping areas are just copied, not redrawn.
	Any newly-visible areas must still be drawn fresh.

	Patch by me in PR#8603, with added comments.

