Sun Apr 25 19:03:40 2004  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* client/connectdlg_common.c, server/civserver.c,
	server/srv_main.c, server/srv_main.h:

	- Add a new server parameter --exit-on-end. If given, the server
	will exit after playing a game rather than restarting. - When the
	client launches a server give it the -q 1 -e parameter. This will
	cause it to quit if the client disconnects.

	Patch by me in PR#8578.

