	always displayed at the top of the worklist. Uses new
	functionality in client/. - Added new SHIFT+Insert shortcut for
	new prepend action. - Added prepend, bubble up, bubble down,
	append buttons.

	Added a buy button to the overview pane.

	Changed the mnemonic of the Trade Routes pane to not clash with
	the mnemonics in the production tab.

	Resolves PR#4340 reported by Per I. Mathisen <per@leftist.net>,
	Raimar Falke <rf13@inf.tu-dresden.de>.

