	branches: 1.15.2; Allow autogen.sh to be run with a separate
	builddir and srcdir.

	Patch by me in PR#8386.

Fri Mar 26 19:44:08 2004  Vasco Alexandre Da Silva Costa <vasc@rnl.ist.utl.pt>:

