	directly, access them via wrappers: unit_build_shield_cost,
	unit_buy_gold_cost, unit_disband_shields, impr_build_shield_cost,
	impr_buy_gold_cost, impr_sell_gold. Behavior is unchanged except
	for the occasional bugfix.

