	data/default/terrain.ruleset, data/history/terrain.ruleset,
	server/maphand.c, server/ruleset.c, server/settlers.c:

	Remove T_RIVER and the ruleset control of river generation. Now
	rivers are always a special (S_RIVER). A new terrain flag
	CanHaveRiver is introduced; this allows the same behavior to be
	reproduced.

