Sun Feb 22 22:32:57 2004  Gregory Berkolaiko <Gregory.Berkolaiko@math.tamu.edu>:

	* ai/advmilitary.c, ai/aitools.c, common/city.h:

	Introduce need_boat field to the ai_choice struct. This field
	indicates that the unit that the city wants to build will need a
	boat. Presently the city will still try to build a boat first,
	but hopefully we will change that soon.

	Patch by Joshua Hudson, part of (PR#6567).

