Thu Feb 19 20:01:07 2004  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* server/barbarian.c, server/citytools.c, server/diplomats.c,
	server/unittools.c, server/unittools.h:

	Pass the unit's transporter to create_unit_full. That way when
	barbarians are created and put on a transporter, the first
	send_unit_info will know about the transporter and won't send
	their info to players who can't see them.

	Bug found by Mateusz Stefek <mstefek@poczta.fm> in PR#7408. Patch
	by me.

