Tue Feb 03 20:21:15 2004  Raimar Falke <i-freeciv-forward@rf.risimo.net>:

	* client/clinet.c, client/gui-gtk-2.0/diplodlg.c,
	client/gui-gtk-2.0/repodlgs.c, common/aicore/aisupport.c,
