Sat Jan 31 17:52:42 2004  Per I. Mathisen <per@leftist.net>:

	* ai/advdiplomacy.c, ai/aitech.c, client/climisc.c,
	client/climisc.h, client/gui-gtk-2.0/diplodlg.c,
	client/gui-gtk-2.0/plrdlg.c, client/gui-gtk-2.0/repodlgs.c,
	client/gui-win32/repodlgs.c, client/gui-xaw/repodlgs.c,
	client/packhand.c, common/capstr.c, common/diptreaty.h,
	common/packets.def, common/packets_gen.c, common/packets_gen.h,
	common/player.c, common/player.h, common/tech.c, common/tech.h,
	server/cityturn.c, server/diplhand.c, server/diplomats.c,
	server/plrhand.c, server/plrhand.h, server/srv_main.c,
	server/unittools.c:

	Team mates now share their research by default. You can opt out
	of this shared research by reducing treaty level to 'alliance'.
	Players also see how much they research for per turn in the
	research dialog, and also how much team mates contribute, if
	anything. For more info, see PR#4213.

