Wed Jan 28 23:08:38 2004  Gregory Berkolaiko <Gregory.Berkolaiko@math.tamu.edu>:

	* ai/aidata.c, ai/aitools.c, ai/aiunit.c, server/unittools.c:

	Various fixes for AI ferries. In particular few exciting bugs
	have been fixed: * ferries should be able to serve settlers now.
	* ferries no longer go to _any_ passanger who wants a ride. They
	only pick up passangers of their own nation. * do counting
	properly.

	For more details, see (PR#7076).

