Mon Nov 10 20:33:58 2003  Raimar Falke <i-freeciv-forward@rf.risimo.net>:

	* client/agents/agents.c, client/civclient.c, common/Makefile.am,
	common/game.c, server/srv_main.c, server/stdinhand.c:

	Cleanup the usage of cm_init() and cm_free(). Previously calls to
	these functions where spread all over the code which resulted in
	memory leaks.

	The only place which calls cm_init() is now game_init() and the
	same for cm_free() and game_free().

