	* client/mapview_common.c:

	Add a function set_mapview_origin() which is called to recenter
	the mapview. This also adds generalized wrapping of the mapview
	(fixing PR#6355), wrapping of the scroll bars, and avoids
	spurious redraws when the mapview origin does not change.

	Issued as PR#6346.

