Wed Sep 17 02:57:21 2003  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* ai/aiair.c, ai/aiunit.c, common/combat.c, common/combat.h,
	server/unithand.c, server/unittools.c:

	Add a new function, can_unit_attack_atll_at_tile. This function
	must pass before a unit can attack any unit on that tile. This
	makes the attack rules more consistent and prevents some
	potential/current bugs.

	Patch by Greg as PR#6132.

