Tue Aug 12 18:54:37 2003  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* client/gui-gtk-2.0/mapview.c, client/mapview_common.c,
	client/tilespec.c, client/tilespec.h:

	When the drawing code assembles a sprite list, each sprite need
	not be aligned with the tile origin but is given its own offset.
	New tileset variables "flag_offset_x" and "flag_offset_y" are
	introduced that provide the offset for flag sprites (which stand
	to benefit most easily from this feature).

	Issued as PR#4576.

