Fri Aug 01 19:58:47 2003  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* client/packhand.c, client/tilespec.c, common/city.h,
	common/packets.c, common/packets.h, server/citytools.c,
	server/maphand.h:

