	* server/settlers.c:

	Use create_unit_virtual to build the virtual units used to find
	good places for terrain improvement and city founding. This makes
	sure all needed fields are initialized; in particular the goto
	destination is cleared.

	Issued as PR#4604.

Fri Jul 18 17:11:18 2003  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* server/citytools.c:

