Fri Jul 11 18:14:11 2003  Gregory Berkolaiko <Gregory.Berkolaiko@math.tamu.edu>:

	* server/userdb/lockfile.c:

	Make sure CVS can be compiled with DEBUG enabled. The problem was
	that lockfile.c never uses freelog(LOG_DEBUG, ...) command which
	triggers "defined and not used" compilation error. Problem is
	solved by adding such a call; it doesn't hurt to have it.

