Wed Jul 02 16:48:55 2003  Per I. Mathisen <per@leftist.net>:

	* common/unit.c:

	When you have sea units with ruleset move rate lower than 2, its
	actual moves in the game is set to 2. This is now fixed so that
	its actual moves is never set higher than its ruleset move rate.

	Bug reported by Bart Coppens (bart@bartcoppens.be).

