Thu Apr 17 21:18:08 2003  Vasco Alexandre Da Silva Costa <vasc@rnl.ist.utl.pt>:

	* client/gui-gtk-2.0/cityrep.c, client/gui-gtk-2.0/dialogs.c,
	client/gui-gtk-2.0/diplodlg.c, client/gui-gtk-2.0/inteldlg.c,
