Wed Apr 16 22:39:09 2003  Vasco Alexandre Da Silva Costa <vasc@rnl.ist.utl.pt>:

	* client/gui-gtk-2.0/citydlg.c:

	* Changed some functions to use their GTK+ 2.0 API equivalents. *
	Changed the layout of the city options. * Changed the font of the
	trade window. * Do not allow selling improvements of an
	investigated city. * Made the production progress bar a GTK+ Drag
	destination. * Removed the change production dialog. Drag items
	from the source view to the production progress bar instead. *
	Changed some labels, added some mnemonics. * NoteBook page
	selection is now done via CTRL+Left/Right. * Added a
	gtk_window_set_role call to the city dialog. This means Window
	Managers should now properly save the dimensions of this dialog.

	Fixes PR#3710.

