Tue Apr 01 16:48:33 2003  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* client/gui-gtk-2.0/mapview.h, client/gui-mui/mapview.h,
	client/gui-sdl/mapview.h, client/gui-win32/mapview.h,
	client/gui-xaw/mapview.h, client/mapctrl_common.c,
	client/mapview_common.c, client/mapview_common.h:

	Remove get_map_xy/get_canvas_xy from the common client code. Now
	map_to_canvas_pos and canvas_to_map_pos do this job. The wrappers
	are still kept as macros on a per-GUI basis.

	Issued as PR#3779.

