Fri Mar 21 23:37:40 2003  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* client/gui-gtk-2.0/citydlg.c, client/gui-gtk-2.0/citydlg.c:

	In the city dialog for the GTK+-1.2 and GTK+-2.0 clients, take
	effects (like Adam Smith's) into account when displaying
	individual and cumulative upkeep for improvements.

