Tue Mar 11 17:59:27 2003  Per I. Mathisen <per@leftist.net>:

	* ai/Makefile.am, client/climisc.c, common/aicore/Makefile.am,
	common/aicore/path_finding.c, common/aicore/path_finding.h,
	common/aicore/pf_tools.c, common/aicore/pf_tools.h, common/map.h,
	common/unit.c, common/unit.h, server/Makefile.am,
	server/maphand.c:

	This adds a new path-finding code. It enables the use of multiple
	path maps at the same time, path iterators and advanced callbacks
	that change the way path-finding is done in real time. No code
	uses this yet.

	Patch by Gregory Berkolaiko and Raimar Falke.

