Thu Mar 06 09:35:12 2003  Raimar Falke <i-freeciv-forward@rf.risimo.net>:

	* client/gui-gtk-2.0/mapview.c, client/gui-mui/mapview.c,
	client/gui-sdl/mapview.c, client/gui-stub/mapview.c,
	client/gui-win32/mapview.c, client/gui-xaw/mapview.c,
