	* m4/sdl-client.m4:

	When checking for the SDL_ttf library, make sure the
	TTF_RenderUNICODE_Blended_Shaded function is available; older
	versions of the library which do not contain this function will
	not suffice.

	Patch by Rafal Bursig as PR#3499.

