Sun Feb 23 12:47:35 2003  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* ai/aicity.c, ai/aihand.c, ai/aiunit.c, common/player.h,
	server/stdinhand.c:

	Introduce an 'away' mode. When a player enters /away from the
	chatline, they toggle away mode. In this AI mode, the ai will run
	the player's civilization but will be unable to make big changes.

	Patch by Per Mathisen as PR#3402.

