Wed Feb 12 01:42:13 2003  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* client/civclient.c:

	Set the coordinates of the PACKET_TURN_DONE packet to (-1,-1).
	Although these values are presumably never used, it is more
	correct and safer to specify explicitly that there is no location
	associated with this packet.

	Issued as PR#3027.

