	server/maphand.h, server/sanitycheck.c, server/savegame.c,
	server/settlers.c, server/unittools.c:

	This patch moves the management of continents back to the server.
	What continent a tile belongs to is no longer considered cheat
	information, and trade routes and effects are resolved from the
	server's omniscient perspective.

	Patch by Mike Kaufman

