	Dorje Short.

Sat Feb 08 22:52:46 2003  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* client/gui-gtk-2.0/mapview.c, client/gui-mui/mapclass.c,
	client/gui-sdl/mapview.c, client/gui-win32/mapview.c,
	client/gui-xaw/mapview.c, client/mapview_common.c:

	Draw city descriptions to the map buffer before flushing them to
	the display. This allows the GUI code to more complex buffering
	systems, as well as giving generally better drawing behavior.

	Issued as PR#2986.

