	* ai/aiair.c:

	Fix bug in aiair code, where wrong function was called with wrong
	parameters.

Sun Feb 02 13:21:50 2003  Raimar Falke <i-freeciv-forward@rf.risimo.net>:

	* ai/advmilitary.c, ai/aidiplomat.c, ai/aiunit.c,
	server/gotohand.c, server/gotohand.h, server/settlers.c:

	Replace warmap's the 2D arrays (indexed by x and y) by a 1D array
	(indexed by map_inx). This is a preparation step for iso maps.

