Fri Jan 31 23:05:52 2003  Eric S Raymond <esr@thyrsus.com>:

	* autogen.sh:

	Generate a Makefile.am file for data/nation based on the contents
	of that directory, so as to avoid having to either hardwire in
	the list of nations or doing wildcarding that breaks `make
	distcheck'. We do this just before calling automake.

