Thu Jan 16 23:16:12 2003  Per I. Mathisen <per@leftist.net>:

	* server/unithand.c, server/unittools.c:

	Add check for non-hostile city on target tile in
	can_unit_attack_unit_at_tile(), and move the same check in
	handle_unit_move_request() above this call so that message
	reporting will still work. This fixes a bug that can happen in AI
	code when a friendly city harbours an enemy unit.

