	if the unit moves _from_ the map position where the focus unit
	is.

	Reported by Thomas Strub <ue80@rz.uni-karlsruhe.de> as (PR#2625).
	Patch from me.

Fri Jan 10 09:38:20 2003  Raimar Falke <i-freeciv-forward@rf.risimo.net>:

	* server/plrhand.c:

	The previous commit stated that "get_invention(x, A_NONE) is
	always TECH_KNOWN". This wasn't true for other players at the
	client. This is fixed now.

