Thu Jan 09 02:36:38 2003  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* ai/advdomestic.c, ai/advmilitary.c, ai/aidata.c,
	ai/aidiplomat.c, ai/aiunit.c, client/goto.c, client/packhand.c,
