	branches: 1.1.2; Provide graphics for technologies (advances) and
	improvements (buildings). The name of the sprite to use is
	specified in the ruleset at the server side, then sent to the
	client where it is loaded from the tileset. Only the SDL client
	uses the graphics at this time.

	Issued as PR#2437. Patch by Rafal Bursig <bursig@poczta.fm> with
