Tue Dec 24 22:42:49 2002  Vasco Alexandre Da Silva Costa <vasc@rnl.ist.utl.pt>:

	* client/gui-gtk-2.0/cityrep.c, client/gui-gtk-2.0/cma_fe.c:

	Renamed some function calls and variable declarations: struct
	cma_parameter -> struct cm_parameter. struct cma_result -> struct
	cm_result. cma_are_parameter_equal() -> cm_are_parameter_equal().
	cma_query_result() -> cm_query_result(). cma_get_stat_name() ->
	cm_get_stat_name().

	This allows one to compile the GTK+ 2.0 client once again after
	the changes made by splitting the calculations part of the CMA
	into general city management code on December the 21st.

