Sat Dec 21 14:19:06 2002  Per I. Mathisen <per@leftist.net>:

	* client/Makefile.am, client/agents/Makefile.am,
	client/agents/agents.c, client/agents/cma_core.c,
	client/agents/cma_core.h, client/agents/cma_fec.c,
	client/agents/cma_fec.h, client/civclient.c,
