Sat Dec 14 10:26:43 2002  Jason Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>:

	* configure.ac, m4/sdl-client.m4:

	Check for -lbind in the server. Check for -lsocket, -lbind, and
	iconv libraries when compiling the SDL client. This improves
	compilation on BeOS and probably other systems.

	Reported by Bernd Korz <bernd.korz@insidebeos.de> PR#2541.

