	server/unittools.c, utility/hash.c, utility/inputfile.c,
	utility/ioz.c, utility/mem.c, utility/shared.c, utility/shared.h:

	Replace fatal-code-error handling (typically abort or
	assert+exit) with a function die() that logs the error,
	(sometimes) dumps core, and then exits. Fatal-user-error cases
	are unchanged.

