	* ai/aiunit.c, ai/aiunit.h, server/citytools.c,
	server/settlers.c:

	Replace use of can_unit_move_to_tile with use of
	could_unit_move_to_tile so that we don't have to be in idle
	activity mode before we consider moving. Also clean up and
	simplify could_unit_move_to_tile a little.

