	client/gui-sdl/wldlg.c, client/gui-sdl/wldlg.h:

	Commit the current code for the SDL client. This code will not
	compile, nor will it run until the graphics are also added. Thus
	this is just a first step.

	All code by Rafal Burseg <bursig@poczta.fm> with modifications by
	myself and Per.

