Tue Nov 26 10:44:09 2002  Raimar Falke <i-freeciv-forward@rf.risimo.net>:

	* m4/debug.m4:

	Remove superfluous adding of "-g" to CFLAGS. This is already done
	by AC_PROG_CC and AC_PROG_CC thinks that the user has supplied
	CFLAGS and so won't change it (it won't for example add -O2 for
	gcc).

	This fixes (PR#2387).

Tue Nov 26 03:12:43 2002  Egbert Hinzen <egbert@hinzen-koeln.de>:

