	attack power from 10 to 15 and increase move rate from 3 to 5.

Mon Nov 25 21:07:42 2002  Vasco Alexandre Da Silva Costa <vasc@rnl.ist.utl.pt>:

	* client/gui-gtk-2.0/plrdlg.c:

	Made several changes to the players dialog: - Changed the colour
	style scheme. Hopefully no more problems. - Stopped using
	GtkTreeModelSort. It is bugged. This means the
	update_players_dialog() algorithm had to be changed. - Don't
	allow sorting the boolean column. - Cleanup.

	Bugs reported by Jason Dorje Short
	<jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>.

Mon Nov 25 19:18:09 2002  Gregory Berkolaiko <Gregory.Berkolaiko@math.tamu.edu>:

