	server/stdinhand.c:

	Enable AI build diplomats for both offence and defence. Add
	H_DIPLOMAT handicap, so that easy and normal AI don't build
	offensive diplomats (diplomats built as a defence can still be
	released to attack).

	Patch by Per I.Mathisen <per@leftist.net>, with few changes by
	me.

