	the city name. This behavior is controlled by a new option which
	is only available if the city names are drawn. Blocked growth and
	no food surplus is also displayed.

	The GTK, GTK2 and Xaw client are changed.

	Patch from Jason Dorje Short <jdorje@users.sourceforge.net>.

