	game: 'Asian' and 'Tropical'. Provide graphics for Trident and
	Isotrident tilesets to support these city styles. Change many
	nations to use a more 'appropriate' city style.

	Graphics and patch by Daniel Speyer <dspeyer@wam.umd.edu>, with
	changes by me.

