Thu Nov 14 09:45:18 2002  Raimar Falke <i-freeciv-forward@rf.risimo.net>:

	* client/gui-gtk-2.0/mapview.c, client/gui-mui/mapview.c,
	client/gui-stub/mapview.c, client/gui-win32/mapview.c,
	client/gui-xaw/mapview.c, client/include/mapview_g.h:

	Add function get_mapview_dimensions which returns the map
	position of the top-left tile and the width and height of the map
	canvas. This information wasn't available to the common code in
	mapview_common previously.

Thu Nov 14 09:28:31 2002  Raimar Falke <i-freeciv-forward@rf.risimo.net>:

	* configure.ac, m4/gettimeofday.m4:

	Replace the static check for gettimeofday at configure time with
	a stricter runtime check. This check tests if the time returned
	by gettimeofday is monotonic and doesn't jump forward by a huge
	amount.

