	* server/sernet.c, server/srv_main.c:

	When the game is over and all players have left, civserver will
	start a new game and wait for new connections instead of exiting.
	The behavior may not be entirely error-free yet, most likely due
	to bugs elsewhere in the code.

	Patch by Per Mathisen.

