Sat Nov 09 22:52:41 2002  Mike Kaufman <kaufman@orion.physics.wisc.edu>:

	* server/citytools.c, server/citytools.c, server/unittools.c,
	server/unittools.c, server/unittools.h, server/unittools.h:

	fix a bug where a core dump happens because player A transfers a
	city to player B but player C allied to A but not B has a unit in
	that city.

	Now those units are transferred to C's closest city, or destroyed
	if one not exist.

	Patch by Davide Pagnin

Fri Nov 08 20:02:01 2002  Raimar Falke <i-freeciv-forward@rf.risimo.net>:

