	* server/unittools.c:

	branches: 1.185.2; Cleanup of enemies_at(), which had the very
	dubious assumption that a city was always dangerous, which in
	turn led to quite unoptimal behaviour and even goto flip flops in
	some cases. Also add a handicap for easy AI that prevents it from
	accurately estimating the strength of the enemy by making use of
	AI omniscience.

