Fri Sep 13 10:04:02 2002  Andreas Kemnade <akemnade@informatik.uni-bremen.de>:

	* utility/shared.c:

	dont't use fopen() in datafilename() to check whether the
	file/directory exists. Some platforms do always return NULL when
	opening a directory using fopen(). So now stat() is used instead

