	truly.

Mon Sep 02 02:19:54 2002  Per I. Mathisen <per@leftist.net>:

	* client/agents/cma_core.c, client/audio_esd.c,
	client/audio_none.c, client/audio_sdl.c, common/capstr.c,
	server/citytools.c, server/gamehand.c, server/report.c,
	server/ruleset.c:

	Initialize uninitialized variables and declare functions
	properly. Now we can compile using gcc with -Wall -Werror
	-Wpointer-arith -Wcast-align -Wstrict-prototypes
	-Wmissing-prototypes -Wnested-externs, and please keep it that
	way :)

	Patch by Sami Liedes, Raimar Falke and myself.

Sun Sep 01 22:44:58 2002  Pieter J. Kersten <kersten@dia.eur.nl>:

	* po/nl.po:

	Updated nl.po

