	Add the ability to choose from a set of string options in the
	local options dialog. A new callback function p_string_vals was
	added to the client options to return this set.

	This new input method is currently used for the audio plugin, the
	soundset and the tileset. For the last two the new function
	datafilelist (in common/shared) was added.

