Mon Jul 29 08:51:00 2002  Raimar Falke <i-freeciv-forward@rf.risimo.net>:

	* server/gotohand.c:

	Initialize all values with DONT_SELECT_ME_FITNESS instead of 0
	since 0 can be valid best_fitness value. Without this change
	every direction can be returned if best_fitness is 0.

	Reported by Jordi Negrevernis i Font <jorneg@retemail.es>. Patch
	from me.

