	* common/map.h, server/stdinhand.c:

	add mapgenerator5: "Generator 5 makes earthlike worlds with one
	or more large continents and a scattering of smaller islands. It
	does so by dividing the world into blocks and on each block
	raising or lowering the corners, then the midpoints and middle
	and so on recursively."

	Patch by Karen Yeats <kayeats@uwaterloo.ca>

