	* configure.ac, m4/debug.m4:

	Concerning debug defaults: In a previous commit, I said I didn't
	change default settings. I lied. This change restores defaults
	and moves debug configure checking into its own macro file. You
	must rerun ./autogen.sh to see these changes, though.

	Thanks to Davide for spotting the error.

