Fri Sep 22 07:24:25 2000  David Pfitzner <dwp@mso.anu.edu.au>:

	* common/city.c, common/city.h, common/game.c, common/log.c,
	common/log.h, common/shared.c, common/shared.h, server/cityhand.c,
	server/ruleset.c:

