Tue Aug  8 12:21:56 2000  David Pfitzner <dwp@mso.anu.edu.au>:

	* client/packhand.c, client/gui-mui/plrdlg.c,
	client/gui-gtk/plrdlg.c, client/gui-xaw/plrdlg.c,
