Wed Jul 19 12:07:34 2000  Jeff Mallatt <jjm@codewell.com>:

	* server/sernet.c:

	With readline, when server is busy it would process one keystroke
	per turn.  This adds a "continue", so that all possible keystrokes
	are processed.

