	* po/ja.po:

	Update ja.po to 1276t+21f+967u+2o.

Sat Jul 15 15:34:26 2000  Jeff Mallatt <jjm@codewell.com>:

	* common/game.c, common/game.h, server/gamehand.c,
	server/stdinhand.c:

	Add support for dispersing initial units over a configurable area.
