	script.  Suggested by David Pfitzner <dwp@mso.anu.edu.au>.

Fri Apr  7 15:03:33 2000  Jeff Mallatt <jjm@codewell.com>:

	* client/gui-gtk/.cvsignore, client/gui-gtk/Makefile.am,
