	connections to barbarian players.  Bug (PR#290, PR#295) reported
	by Rizos Sakellariou <rizos@rice.edu>, Tuomas Airaksinen
	<tuma@linuxfan.com>, and others.  Patch submitted by Reinier Post
	<rp@win.tue.nl>.

