Thu Feb 10 23:55:31 2000  Jeff Mallatt <jjm@codewell.com>:

	* configure, configure.in, client/gui-xaw/Freeciv.h,
	common/version.h, data/Freeciv, po/de.po, po/en_GB.po, po/es.po,
