Fri Aug 13 19:26:36 1999  Jeff Mallatt <jjm@codewell.com>:

	* client/packhand.c, client/gui-gtk/dialogs.c,
	client/gui-gtk/repodlgs.c, client/gui-xaw/dialogs.c,
